;; duplicate inequalities)
;;
;; decides satisfiability, implication, etc... of/between sets of linear inequalities
;; of the form ([(a_1x_1 + a_2x_2 + ... + a_c) <= (b_1x_1 + b_2x_2 + ... + b_c)] ...)
